Project Title: User Registration Form

User Registration Form is a user-friendly web application crafted with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, designed for hassle-free user registration.
The form collects essential information including Name, Age, Gender, Email ID, and a user photo upload option.
The JavaScript functionality ensures input validation, verifying accurate data entry and proper email formats. 
Upon submission, the entered details are dynamically displayed on the page, offering users immediate feedback. 
The form's responsive design guarantees a consistent and visually pleasing layout across devices. 
With clear error handling, age verification, and an emphasis on aesthetics, RegiForm provides an efficient and visually appealing solution for user data input and display.
